OL,3,CCouple renew their vows in care home
OL,4,C50 years after their first wedding
OL,6,FA couple from Torquay have renewed
OL,7,Ftheir wedding vows in a care home - 50
OL,8,Fyears after they first tied the knot.
OL,10,FMarita Hanson finds it difficult to
OL,11,Fremember her first wedding to John
OL,12,Fbecause of dementia, so John and their
OL,13,Fdaughter Victoria Hanson-Hughes
OL,14,Fdecided to give her a second wedding
OL,15,Fday .
OL,17,FThe ceremony was held on Saturday 13
OL,18,FJuly at Lorna House Residential Home
OL,19,Fin Babbacombe, where Mrs Hanson lives.
