OL,3,CCouple renew their vows in care home
OL,4,C50 years after their first wedding
OL,6,FMs Hanson-Hughes said: "It was just
OL,7,Flike a wedding day all over again.
OL,8,FEveryone at Lorna House went all out
OL,9,Fto make it an amazing day and I had
OL,10,Fwonderful support from friends and
OL,11,Ffamily to make it a day of love,
OL,12,Femotions and smiles all around."
OL,14,FA nearby Barnados charity shop lend
OL,15,FVictoria a mannequin to display her
OL,16,Fmum's original wedding dress.
