OL,3,CCouple renew their vows in care home
OL,4,C50 years after their first wedding
OL,6,FMs Hanson Hughes said: "It all went so
OL,7,Fsmoothly and everyone involved had a
OL,8,Fgreat day, the residents all dressed
OL,9,Ffor the occasion and had fascinators
OL,10,Fin their hair and wore smiles from
OL,11,Fcheek to cheek."
OL,13,FThe couple first met as children as
OL,14,FMarita went to school with John's
OL,15,Fsister Christine. At that first
OL,16,Fmeeting John was covered in chocolate,
OL,17,Fwhich was supposed to be a present for
OL,18,Fhis sister, but he'd polished it off
OL,19,Fbecause she was late back from school.
