OL,3,CCouple renew their vows in care home
OL,4,C50 years after their first wedding
OL,6,FTheir first date, a few years later,
OL,7,Fwas arranged by Christine at a
OL,8,FValentine's disco in their local Mecca.
OL,10,FAfter a few years dating they wanted
OL,11,Fto go camping but Marita's mother said
OL,12,Fno, so with that they went and booked
OL,13,Fa wedding and got married.
OL,15,FVictoria said: "Even with mum's
OL,16,Fparents against them and this horrible
OL,17,Fdisease stealing their retirement from
OL,18,Fthem, more than 50 years later they
OL,19,Fare still together.
