OL,3,CCouple renew their vows in care home
OL,4,C50 years after their first wedding
OL,6,F"I asked the staff at Lorna house for
OL,7,Ftheir permission to lay on a small
OL,8,Fevent in their garden. They not only
OL,9,Fsaid yes but they have gone over and
OL,10,Fabove in helping organise the best day
OL,11,Ffor my parents.
OL,13,F"It's not just about us now but mum's
OL,14,Fextended Lorna house family as well,
OL,15,Fthey are all so kind from helping to
OL,16,Fdecorate the space and supplying
OL,17,Fchairs, a marquee and a marriage arch
OL,18,Fand even supplying support so mum and
OL,19,Fdad can have a night in a local hotel."
